## Setting up tint2 in fluxbox ##

# http://fluxbox.org/help/man-fluxbox.php
# https://gitlab.com/o9000/tint2/blob/master/doc/tint2.md
# https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Tint2#Running_tint2

1. edit and enable tint2 in : ~/.fluxbox/startup

2. edit : ~/.fluxbox/init
   Change : session.screen0.toolbar.tools:	workspacename, iconbar, systemtray, clock
   To     : session.screen0.toolbar.tools:	workspacename, iconbar, clock   

   Change : session.screen0.toolbar.layer:	Dock
   To     : session.screen0.toolbar.layer:	Desktop
   
   Change : session.screen0.toolbar.visible:	true
   To     : session.screen0.toolbar.visible:	false 
